2. Project Summary
   2.1. Project Description:
   
	This case is a part of the sun4v umbrella case
	FWARC/2004/510.

	This case defines the core CPU and memory API for sun4v.
	
	These APIs present abstractions to guest FW (such as OBP)
	and OS (such as solaris) SW in several core areas.  The
	main areas covered by this API are:

	- CPU management

	- MMU management

	- virtual machine management

	- virtual console and TOD devices

